&lt;h1 id=&#34;pythonistahttpomz-softwarecompythonistaindexhtml&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://omz-software.com/pythonista/index.html&#34;target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Pythonista&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
